Package: dennco-novnc-clipboard-panel
Version: 0.1.1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Dennco Information Systems <dustinbayn@denncoholdingcompany.com>
Depends: bash, sed, coreutils
Description: Dennco clipboard panel overlay for Proxmox noVNC
 Adds a browser-side clipboard panel to the Proxmox noVNC console.
 This package installs JavaScript and CSS overlay files and injects them
 into the local noVNC console page.
